	ith several skaters from specified seating sections. Due to this event tak
	ing place prior to doors opening\, EVERYONE entering the venue early must 
	have an event ticket AND Pre-Show Stargazer Pass for entry. This includes 
	all children as well as the parent(s)/guardian(s) wishing to accompany the
